V0506_01_00_01_1.text: But if you wish to fight, you're leaving me with no choice!

V0506_01_00_02_0.text: My Phantom Knights have no fear on the battlefield!

V0506_01_00_03_0.text: You'll learn just how powerful Xyz Monsters can be!

V0506_01_00_04_0.text: Dark Rebellion and I will fight you together!

V0506_01_00_06_0.text:
Lay down your Duel Disk.
Or you'll force me to Duel.

V0506_01_00_07_0.text: Lulu, you taught me to Duel for joy instead of hate.

V0506_05_00_00_0.text: Like my Phantom Knights, I always rise to fight again!

V0506_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0506_11_01_00_0.text: I summon my monster in Defense Position!

V0506_11_08_01_0.text:
I build the Overlay Network!
Xyz Summon!

V0506_16_00_01_0.text: The battlefield is no place for the meek!

V0506_21_00_00_1.text:
Didn't you hear me?
I ended my turn.

V0506_21_00_01_0.text: I thought you'd pose more of a challenge.

V0506_21_00_03_0.text: That brings my turn to an end.

V0506_21_00_04_1.text: Do whatever you feel is right.

V0506_28_00_00_0.text: I fight to protect the future.

V0506_28_00_01_0.text: My Phantom Knights may fall, but they always get back up!

V0506_28_00_02_0.text: Nothing about your Duel had me worried.

V0506_28_00_02_1.text: Not your cards - nor your tactics.

V0506_28_00_03_0.text: Your strategy was so obvious that I thought you were joking.

V0506_28_00_04_0.text: This is the power of my Dark Rebellion!

V0506_28_00_05_0.text: I do admire your desire to help your friends.

V0506_28_00_06_0.text: Our Duel should be fun for everyone.

V0506_29_00_01_0.text: I can't make anyone smile if I Duel like this.

V0506_29_00_02_0.text: My Phantom Knights can't stand anymore...

V0506_29_00_04_0.text: Always remember to keep the world entertained and smiling.

V0506_29_00_05_0.text:
Your Lyrilusc Deck is great!
How did you come up with it?

V0506_33_00_01_0.text: My deck will unleash its true strength!

V0506_33_00_02_0.text: This will strike you straight to your core!

V0506_30_00_00_0.text: You pose no threat to me.

V0506_30_00_01_0.text: When I have monsters with the same Level, you're in trouble!

V0506_30_00_02_0.text: Overlay Units are key to unlocking my Xyz Monsters' power!

V0506_34_00_01_0.text: I don't wanna hurt anyone anymore…

V0506_34_00_02_0.text: This card is too good for you.

V0506_34_00_03_0.text: I don't wanna harm you - even if you are my foe.

V0506_34_00_04_0.text: If you surrender, you can end your suffering.

V0506_34_00_05_0.text: A single crack will cause your entire strategy to crumble.

V0506_34_00_06_0.text: Don't worry. There are doctors in Duel Links to heal you up.

V0506_34_00_07_0.text: This Duel has lost all meaning.

V0506_34_00_08_0.text: I'll finish you! And destroy everything!

V0506_34_00_10_0.text: Use your power... to keep the world smiling...

V0506_35_00_00_0.text: I'm Yuto from the Xyz Dimension.

V0506_35_00_01_0.text: The Phantom Knights cannot be conquered!

V0506_36_00_04_0.text: Shay! I know you can win this Duel!
